---
title: "US41 — Register / apply as expert"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>Expert Application Page (website)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SubmitExpertApplication
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile · ExpertVerificationDocument
  A->>B: fill professional details, attach credential files, tap SUBMIT
  B->>C: submit(application, files)
  C->>E: uploadVerificationDocument(file)
  E-->>C: ExpertVerificationDocument (storage path)
  C->>E: submitExpertApplication(application, docIds)
  alt submitted
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (status = pending)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (submitted)
    B-->>A: "application under review"
  else upload / insert failed
    E-->>C: StorageException / PostgrestException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not submit application. Try again."
  end
  note over E: uploadVerificationDocument via StorageGateway → expert-docs bucket.<br/>submitExpertApplication via SupabaseGateway → expert_profiles (RLS)
